
//*******************************************
//building
//*******************************************

hopefully, there are only 4 steps to build:
1. 
    In the same folder as this README, use bash to
    run build_solution.

    ./build_solution

2.
    Go into the folder ./external/cgal/ and open up
    CGAL.sln

    right click on ALL_BUILD and build the entire solution

3.
    Go back to the same folder as this README, open up Convexify.sln 

    right click on ALL_BUILD and build the entire solution

4.
    set convexifyEXE as the startup project and run it

    f5
